description: Cross-company competitive intelligence command center. One Intel Director orchestrates an Analyst and a Signal Scout to watch every competitor — pricing, releases, positioning, funding, hiring, reviews — and publish daily signal scans, weekly competitor briefings, and a monthly landscape review. Every move is captured as an inspectable file.
